{"tid":562032,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇比父母將你屋企啲野講比班親戚聽？","createTime":"2018-02-15T13:51:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-15T13:53:42.000Z","uid":164255,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"186aa1ef0e3ae9cd7add8015c2608c201a0f8390","tid":562032,"uid":164255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T13:51:12.000Z","msg":"今晚食團年飯 老豆冇啦啦開口話我係屋企冇禮貌<br />\n有時佢唔講道理先咁咪反駁佢<br />\n點知岩岩比佢講話我駁嘴駁舌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 乜乜柒柒 總知就講到我冇禮貌 不孝女咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成班親戚就跟住話：哇 呢家啲小朋友係咁咖啦 又唔打得又冇禮貌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想搵窿捐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d2b6aedb5fed84efb3ed262e2ec6ca1c0b301d8","tid":562032,"uid":164255,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T13:52:47.000Z","msg":"佢地口中既小朋友唔係小中學個啲 係做人仔女個啲小朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a6962e2f6726944e71387c484ab610737af284e","tid":562032,"uid":8302,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T13:53:42.000Z","msg":"問佢望乜撚野"}]}